column2: SELECT TOP # a.apogee_id,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,a.snr,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,a.verr,a.verr_med, #,#  FROM apogeeStar as a JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq(#,#,#/#) AS b ON b.apstar_id = a.apstar_id  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id UNION ALL SELECT TOP # a.apogee_id,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,a.snr,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,a.verr,a.verr_med, #,#  FROM apogeeStar as a JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq(#,#,#/#) AS b ON b.apstar_id = a.apstar_id  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id
